A_1(x) &amp;amp;= a_0 + a_2 x + a_4 x^2 + ... + a_n x^{\frac{n}{2}}
\\

A_2(x) &amp;amp;= a_1 + a_3 x + a_5 x^2 + ... + a_{n-1} x^{\frac{n}{2}-1} 

\end{aligned}
